they're well en

46:39.597 --> 46:40.831 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
route to.

46:40.865 --> 46:43.267 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
That was at the forefront of his
mind.

46:43.300 --> 46:47.438 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And you could see that twinkle
