51:06.096 --> 51:10.301 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But he realized that for a tenor
to sing a
high B-flat for 10 beats eight
times a week

51:10.334 --> 51:11.769 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
