material.

51:11.802 --> 51:14.772 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: So that's gone
from the musical.

51:14.805 --> 51:15.773 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
ROB KAPILOW: That's gone.

51:15.806 --> 51:16.774 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
They lowered it in pitch.

51:16.807 --> 51:18.442 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
He doesn't have to sing the high
notes

51:18.475 --> 51:22.780 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But, interestingly, later in his
life, in
his head, he thought, I really
do want to

51:22.813 --> 51:27.017 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
